  "body": {
    "view": {
      "representation": "view",
      "value": "<div class=\"contentLayout2\">\n<div class=\"columnLayout fixed-width\" data-layout=\"fixed-width\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<div class=\"confluence-information-macro confluence-information-macro-note conf-macro output-block\" data-hasbody=\"true\" data-macro-id=\"0fb20e33-0217-4b0b-a6be-216976c9323a\" data-macro-name=\"note\"><span class=\"aui-icon aui-icon-small aui-iconfont-warning confluence-information-macro-icon\"> </span><div class=\"confluence-information-macro-body\"><p>In the parameters below, some of them can be overridden by a <a href=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/REN27/pages/542217837/PxrLayer\" rel=\"nofollow\">PxrLayer</a> when connected to the <strong>Input Material </strong>or through a <a href=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/REN27/pages/542218974/PxrLayerMixer\" rel=\"nofollow\">PxrLayerMixer</a>. <a href=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/REN27/pages/542216714/PxrLayerSurface\" rel=\"nofollow\">PxrLayerSurface</a> is designed to better illustrate which parameters are not able to be overridden in a layer by including only parameters that are global. We recommend this material when you know you will be layering. The results of these settings are unchanged.</p><ul><li><p><strong>Bold Face</strong> parameters are layerable, able to be overridden per layer.</p></li><li><p><em>Italicized</em> parameters are not able to be layered or overridden. These are globally obeyed for all layers. For example: Choosing GGX as a specular model will mean all layers will be GGX for that parameter.</p></li></ul></div></div><h3 id=\"GlowParameters-GlowParameters\">Glow Parameters</h3><p>Glow can make an object <em>appear</em> to emit light. This is useful when you need a textured effect like lit panels, circuitry, lava, or other complex effects with local influence in lighting.</p><div class=\"confluence-information-macro confluence-information-macro-note conf-macro output-block\" data-hasbody=\"true\" data-macro-id=\"29c6c973-f9f6-4458-b9c4-44aa9cb387e2\" data-macro-name=\"note\"><span class=\"aui-icon aui-icon-small aui-iconfont-warning confluence-information-macro-icon\"> </span><div class=\"confluence-information-macro-body\"><p>This is not an efficient way to light a scene and would require indirect bounces to be at least 2 to be effective. We recommend this as a textured effect and not for actual lighting.</p></div></div><p><br/></p><p><strong>Gain</strong></p><p>Glow gain or weight. Below we go from the default grey material and increase the gain (using white color) to 0.5 and then 1.0.</p><p><br/></p></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout three-equal\" data-layout=\"three-equal\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-left-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-left\" width=\"463\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542216653/rman_pxrsurf_glowGain00.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330510881&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=384\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/542216653/rman_pxrsurf_glowGain00.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330510881&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"384\" data-width=\"384\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"542216671\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"rman_pxrsurf_glowGain00.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"542216653\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"c4d32adf-814d-4765-9044-27136a7cedc6\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542216653/rman_pxrsurf_glowGain00.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330510881&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=384 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542216653/rman_pxrsurf_glowGain00.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330510881&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=384 1x\"></span></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-left-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-left\" width=\"463\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542216653/rman_pxrsurf_glowGain05.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330510881&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=384\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/542216653/rman_pxrsurf_glowGain05.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330510881&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"384\" data-width=\"384\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"542216674\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"rman_pxrsurf_glowGain05.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"542216653\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"ed7237ac-ed46-4882-bc3a-df63f99eed58\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542216653/rman_pxrsurf_glowGain05.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330510881&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=384 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542216653/rman_pxrsurf_glowGain05.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330510881&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=384 1x\"></span></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-left-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-left\" width=\"463\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542216653/rman_pxrsurf_glowGain10.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330510881&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=384\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/542216653/rman_pxrsurf_glowGain10.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330510881&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"384\" data-width=\"384\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"542216677\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"rman_pxrsurf_glowGain10.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"542216653\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"d9e7596b-c415-4298-ae5b-56aa8f389ed4\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542216653/rman_pxrsurf_glowGain10.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330510881&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=384 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542216653/rman_pxrsurf_glowGain10.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330510881&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=384 1x\"></span></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout fixed-width\" data-layout=\"fixed-width\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<p><br/></p><p><strong>Color</strong></p><p>Controls the incandescence color, or glow, of the material. Below are various examples of textured inputs to the Color parameter.</p><p><br/></p></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout three-equal\" data-layout=\"three-equal\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-left-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-left\" width=\"463\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542216653/rman_pxrsurf_glowColor3.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330511105&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=384\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/542216653/rman_pxrsurf_glowColor3.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330511105&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"384\" data-width=\"384\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"542216686\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"rman_pxrsurf_glowColor3.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"542216653\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"df90e0a4-bded-452b-aea0-bd72cb0b4143\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542216653/rman_pxrsurf_glowColor3.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330511105&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=384 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542216653/rman_pxrsurf_glowColor3.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330511105&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=384 1x\"></span></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-left-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-left\" width=\"463\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassi